\nTenshi to Seijo (Angel and Bible)\nThe court shuffle matches between Courts 3 and 5 pairs Rikkai''s Akaya Kirihara and Shitenhouji''s Kuranosuke Shiraishi together. As the game grows progressively more difficult, Kirihara becomes agitated by their opponents. Remembering a promise he made to Kirihara''s teammate, Shiraishi must prevent the young boy from losing control of his temper at all costs.\n\nHimitsu no Oujisama (Prince of Secrets)\nThe middle schoolers become restless and irritated when the camp''s food supply begins to run low from a harsh storm. Seishun Academy''s Satoshi Horio must deliver a bag to his teammate, Ryouma Echizen, but the angry middle schoolers start to believe that he is hiding food from them. In an attempt to claim the bag''s contents, they all begin to fight each other as Horio tries to outsmart and run past them.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "broadcast": {"day": null, "time": null, "string": null, "timezone": null}, "favorites": 15, "licensors": [], "producers": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/16/TV_Tokyo", "name": "TV Tokyo", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 16}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/23/Bandai_Visual", "name": "Bandai Visual", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 23}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/139/Nihon_Ad_Systems", "name": "Nihon Ad Systems", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 139}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/751/Marvelous_AQL", "name": "Marvelous AQL", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 751}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/1365/Shueisha", "name": "Shueisha", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 1365}], "relations": [{"entry": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/manga/12965/Shin_Tennis_no_Oujisama", "name": "Shin Tennis no Oujisama", "type": "manga", "mal_id": 12965}], "relation": "Adaptation"}, {"entry": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/11371/Shin_Tennis_no_Oujisama", "name": "Shin Tennis no Oujisama", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 11371}], "relation": "Parent Story"}],